Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.63,0:00:11.40,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.14,0:00:17.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,照亮了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.95,0:00:30.02,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:36.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:44.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.17,0:00:51.41,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:01:00.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.15,0:01:05.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:10.59,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.66,0:01:15.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:22.77,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.11,0:01:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时值公元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.28,0:01:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,经历重重冒险之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.75,0:01:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强与娜蒂亚他们以及三人组 开始了在鹦鹉螺号上的新生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.09,0:01:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尽管因为不习惯潜水艇的生活 而感到有些不适应
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.89,0:01:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但强他们仍坚强地面对 每天的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号今天也为了追赶 神秘组织『新亚特兰提斯』
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而在海中航行…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.77,0:01:49.79,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,#12 葛兰迪丝的初恋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:02:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号上的机械真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.98,0:02:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不一会儿就把金属切开了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快看快看 桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.99,0:02:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,韩森 我们已经在这艘船上 待几天了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个嘛 一直待在船里头 我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只能从吃了几顿饭来算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 最过份的就是伙食
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早上吃鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,中午吃鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晚上也吃鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无论醒着还是睡着 全都是鱼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底还要吃鱼吃到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我并不介意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大姐头也那么起劲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉人也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,偏偏带头的大姐头 也一头栽进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也别愣在那里 快点换衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.60,0:02:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用不着谢我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为你那身土里土气的穿着 跟我站在一起会很不搭调
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别拖拖拉拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再不快点我就来不及帮 心爱的尼莫先生准备餐点了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你等着吧 尼莫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一定会用我的爱 来填满你的胃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,动作快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请趁热享用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我今天特别用心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,味道还满意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我的光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.73,0:04:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王也快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如何？好看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是用葛兰迪丝的旧衣服 修改而成的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好漂亮喔 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你觉得怎么样？强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉也老是说我没规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗 我不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她是在生什么气？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:05:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,女孩子真教人摸不透
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呆头鹅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我受不了了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我再也忍不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每天每天都是鱼鱼鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经受够吃鱼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不光是鱼的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每天都窝在这艘船里头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算做了新西装 我也高兴不起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,餐点偶尔也该供应些 带血的牛排啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你别太过份了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上哪去找那种东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也不晓得我为了变换菜色 有多头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他最近才上船过这种生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想发发牢骚也怪不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也只能忍耐到习惯这种生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到时候他就不会抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,厨师长说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果想要和我们共同行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就必须习惯这里的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 我很满意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就算每天吃鱼也不要紧 艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每天都吃同样的菜色 是辛苦了点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但还是请多忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 你那是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是对我有意见吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 我说了什么 会让你不舒服的话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫先生 还有甜点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我费心做的甜点…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都是因为你多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才会让尼莫先生不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么这样…怪我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是诚实表达 自己的感受…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给我住口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是你真那么不爱吃鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就吃这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们两个都别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这件事与你无关
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别跑 桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别闹了 大家都别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都好没规矩喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,脾气似乎愈来愈火爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 我没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是指那群人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可能是还没适应新环境吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果今天没碰到长嘴硬鳞鱼号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就将明天订为狩猎日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也会一同参与
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:07:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,岛？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说可以登陆了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两舷停止 固定鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全锚到底
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,固定完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全员可以开始登陆了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呀吼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天可以吃到肉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉不一起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已经有人出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 我们也快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 你不是比较喜欢 在艾丽朵拉那里看书吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并…并不是那样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧 大王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到鹦鹉螺号里有那么多人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的 平常根本没机会见面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一眼望去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里聚集了好多国家的人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,白人与黑人能和睦相处 实在难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船也可以说是一个理想国度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每个人对事物的看法与想法 必然不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以要每个人都能认同他人 平等相处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是件极不容易的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这艘船里头的人不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都是为了同一个目标 而聚集在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.56,0:10:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同一个目标？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是消灭新亚特兰提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我话似乎多了点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们也下船去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大姐头也稍微帮点忙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人家可是千金小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从没拿过比刀叉还重的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到他也来了 该怎么办好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:10:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说不定今晚我能与尼莫先生 一起在海边…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不能耗在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要出击 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恋爱中的女人真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉不一起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最近的年轻人真是的 一点都不懂得含蓄之美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的 所以大家都说 恋爱中的女人可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 船长能得到人家 那么积极的追求
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也算是不枉生为男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然嘴上不饶人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但葛兰迪丝也确实是个美人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加上身材也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且料理的手艺也不在话下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.29,0:11:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然卖相糟了点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要是再年轻个10岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 年轻个20岁的话 一定会主动去追她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 船长会到岛上去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就表示八字有一撇啰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.81,0:12:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真要是那样事情就有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也要到岛上去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来的任务就麻烦两位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 她终于去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,偶尔也该把新亚特兰提斯 抛在脑后啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真希望副船长 也能诚实面对自己的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多学学那位葛兰迪丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然尼莫先生也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就非得用这东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这下子他一定会迷上我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,星空之下 夜晚的海边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谱出只属于两人的恋曲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要加把劲 加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小孩子到一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.27,0:13:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森 你竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然打中了\N你也挺行的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好意思 打扰一下各位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请问尼莫先生到哪里去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不晓得耶 我没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长去调查附近一带了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 你不是要留在船上吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.01,0:14:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不巧 有些事情得处理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还想让他瞧瞧这件泳装的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也该想想自己的年纪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直穿着泳装会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用你多嘴 你这个碍事的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才二十多岁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.53,0:15:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 经过四舍五入 早就到三十大关了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用你多事 那你又是几岁？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,经过四舍五入 本人恰好二十岁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反正一定是你谎报年龄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.02,0:15:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沙子好烫 而且一踩就会沉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我都不晓得踩在沙子上 原来这么有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 因为一直都踏在 潜水艇的金属地板上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你看 好美的贝壳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.91,0:15:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好美的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若是将我的心譬喻成那只 飘荡于天地间的海鸥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.28,0:16:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你就是大海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝小姐 有件事我必须先跟你说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我将这座岛的资料拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 打扰到两位了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫先生 请继续说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 还是下次再找机会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,副船长\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我先回鹦鹉螺号了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:17:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长跟副船长 不能同时都不在船上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你一直穿成那样 小心会感冒的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天一定要吃到…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肉 肉 肉 肉.肉！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真想早点吃到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 你们就好好期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 强他们要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打猎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打猎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要再熬煮一下就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝小姐 原来女人该会的你都会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.84,0:18:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再怎么说我都是个千金小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,除了跑跑跳跳 你也该学点其它的才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就是笨手笨脚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都尊称我『大小姐』的 那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,身为拥有大铁矿的 格兰家独生女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从小就备受宠爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈她身体不好 在我很小的时候就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她留给我们的是 快乐的回忆与宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也因为这样 我成了爸爸唯一的心肝宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他真的是把我宠上天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每天都过着幸福的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.43,0:18:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,后来我长大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,16岁初次参加舞会的夜里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我遇到了一名男子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是个有地位又有名望的贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们立刻坠入爱河
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不顾爸爸的反对 跟他订了婚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那男人是个大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本不是什么贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是为了爸爸的财产才接近我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸为那个人作保
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被迫支付大笔债款
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一切都是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不光是遭到初恋情人背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还失去了原本的家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.13,0:20:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,过去那些对我阿谀奉承的人 一个个走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只剩下担任司机的桑森 与技师韩森
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有妈妈留下来的宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最后救了我们的 还是妈妈的宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,宝石以它的美貌 为我们换来金钱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很感激
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:30.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为宝石没有背叛我的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那时我就下定了决心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只为宝石而活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一定要得到 世界上最美的宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不会再打你宝贝的 蔚蓝之水的歪主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我找到别的人生目标了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.04,0:20:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那位先生正是海中宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,男人中的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:20:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道你珍惜蔚蓝之水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 强是个 更值得你珍惜的人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.06,0:21:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是个难得愿意 一直陪着你这种女孩的人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.86,0:21:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要对他好一点才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强只是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家一开始都是那么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但总有一天 你会对他心怀感激
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人是没办法独自活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来是你们 没事别吓人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.96,0:21:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们看 你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都满载而归喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.00,0:21:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们看 是肉喔 肉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以就说男人糟糕嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真想让你们吃吃 尼莫船长的指甲垢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 你真的好厉害 桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一枪就毙命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.12,0:22:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可是个射击天才呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家来享用小鹿排吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.99,0:22:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是你们杀死它的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.03,0:22:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它还只是个孩子耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们都不觉得它可怜吗？ 竟然还做出这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.41,0:22:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌 讨厌 我最讨厌你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.58,0:22:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.68,0:22:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她是在生什么气？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,女生真教人搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有人… 没有人能够了解我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.40,0:22:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要 别过来 到那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.70,0:22:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一直都是一个人活过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.87,0:23:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以后当然也能一个人活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.65,0:23:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起 对不起 大王
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.22,0:23:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我好寂寞 其实我好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.21,0:23:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.45,0:23:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心脏突然跳得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.09,0:23:54.62,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.69,0:24:02.73,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.80,0:24:07.83,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.91,0:24:12.28,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.34,0:24:21.12,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.19,0:24:31.29,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.36,0:24:40.07,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.14,0:24:44.34,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.41,0:24:49.01,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.08,0:24:58.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.93,0:25:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉跟大王 从岛上的营地消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.40,0:25:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真无聊 娜蒂亚与强一直在吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.37,0:25:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王 是海耶
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.88,0:25:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以看到海 还有鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.71,0:25:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.72,0:25:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『跑啊！玛莉』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.46,0:25:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要看喔
